19-- ----------------------  Content type
20
21-- | Shorthand function for the Baala content type.
22--
23--   >>> the $ D.pText "a"
24--   VText "a"
25--
26the :: BaalaC -> BaalaC
27{-# INLINE the #-}
28the = id
29
30-- | The Baala content type.
31data BaalaC
32    = VBool    Bool               -- ^ Boolean type
33    | VCode    String             -- ^ Code type
34    | VText    String             -- ^ String type
35    | VTerm    String             -- ^ Term name type
36    | VDec     D.Decimal          -- ^ Decimal number type
37    | VClock   D.Clock            -- ^ Clock type
38    | VTime    D.Time             -- ^ Time type
39    | VEmpty                      -- ^ Sign of no ordinary type
40    | VEnd                        -- ^ The end of everything
41    | VInterp  D.Interp           -- ^ Interpretation type
42    | VType    D.Type             -- ^ Type for type
43    | VList    [BaalaC]           -- ^ List type (objective collection)
44    | VSet     [BaalaC]           -- ^ Set type (informative collection)
45    | VTie     [B.Named BaalaC]   -- ^ Tie type (set of terms)
46    | VRel     (D.Rel BaalaC)     -- ^ Relation type
47    deriving (Show)
48
49instance Eq BaalaC where
50    x == y  = compare x y == EQ
51    x /= y  = compare x y /= EQ
52
53instance Ord BaalaC where
54    -- simple
55    compare (VBool    x) (VBool    y)  = compare x y
56    compare (VDec     x) (VDec     y)  = compare x y
57    compare (VClock   x) (VClock   y)  = compare x y
58    compare (VTime    x) (VTime    y)  = compare x y
59    compare (VCode    x) (VCode    y)  = compare x y
60    compare (VTerm    x) (VTerm    y)  = compare x y
61    compare (VText    x) (VText    y)  = compare x y
62
63    -- complex
64    compare (VList    x) (VList    y)  = compare x y
65    compare (VSet     x) (VSet     y)  = compareAsSet x y
66    compare (VTie     x) (VTie     y)  = compareAsSet x y
67    compare (VRel     x) (VRel     y)  = compare x y
68    compare (VInterp  x) (VInterp  y)  = compare x y
69    compare (VType    x) (VType    y)  = compare x y
70
71    -- others
72    compare x y  = D.typeOrder x `compare` D.typeOrder y
73
74compareAsSet :: (Ord a) => [a] -> [a] -> Ordering
75compareAsSet x y = compare (Set.fromList x) (Set.fromList y)
76
77instance D.CTypeOf BaalaC where
78    typeOf (VBool    _)  = D.TypeBool
79    typeOf (VCode    _)  = D.TypeCode
80    typeOf (VText    _)  = D.TypeText
81    typeOf (VTerm    _)  = D.TypeTerm
82    typeOf (VDec     _)  = D.TypeDec
83    typeOf (VClock   c)  = D.TypeClock $ Just $ D.clockPrecision c
84    typeOf (VTime    t)  = D.TypeTime  $ Just $ D.timePrecision t
85    typeOf (VEmpty    )  = D.TypeEmpty
86    typeOf (VEnd      )  = D.TypeEnd
87    typeOf (VInterp  _)  = D.TypeInterp
88    typeOf (VType    _)  = D.TypeType
89    typeOf (VList   cs)  = D.TypeList $ typeSum cs
90    typeOf (VSet    cs)  = D.TypeSet  $ typeSum cs
91    typeOf (VTie    cs)  = D.TypeTie  $ B.mapSndTo D.typeOf cs
92    typeOf (VRel     _)  = D.TypeRel []
93
94typeSum :: D.CTypeOf c => [c] -> D.Type
95typeSum cs = case B.unique $ map D.typeOf cs of
96               [t] -> t
97               ts  -> D.TypeSum ts
98
99instance D.CContent BaalaC where
100    appendContent (VEmpty) x           = Right x
101    appendContent x (VEmpty)           = Right x
102    appendContent (VText x) (VText y)  = Right . VText $ x ++ y
103    appendContent x y                  = Msg.unmatchType (show (x, y))
104
105instance B.MixShortEncode BaalaC where
106    mixShortEncode sh c =
107        case c of
108          VCode  s   -> B.mixString $ quote  (sh s) s
109          VText  s   -> B.mixString $ qquote (sh s) s
110          VTerm  s   -> B.mixString $ "'/" ++ s
111          VDec   n   -> B.mixString $ D.encodeDecimal n
112          VClock t   -> B.mixEncode t
113          VTime  t   -> B.mixEncode t
114          VBool  b   -> B.mixEncode b
115          VEmpty     -> B.mixString "()"
116          VEnd       -> B.mixString "(/)"
117
118          VList cs   -> D.mixBracketList $ mixBar cs
119          VSet  cs   -> D.mixBracketSet  $ mixBar cs
120          VTie  ts   -> B.mixBracketS S.tieOpen  S.tieClose  $ D.termsToMix1 sh ts
121          VRel  r    -> B.mixShortEncode sh r
122          VInterp i  -> B.mixEncode i
123          VType t    -> B.mixBracketS S.typeOpen S.typeClose $ B.mixEncode t
124        where
125          mixBar cs   = B.mixJoinBar $ map (B.mixShortEncode sh) cs
126
127quote :: Maybe String -> String -> String
128quote (Nothing) s   = "'" ++ s
129quote (Just s)  _   = s
130
131qquote :: Maybe String -> String -> String
132qquote (Nothing) "" = "\"\""
133qquote (Nothing) s  = S.angleQuote s
134qquote (Just s)  _  = s
135

137-- ----------------------  haskell data
138
139instance D.CBool BaalaC where
140    pBool                    = VBool
141    gBool (VBool x)          = x
142    gBool _                  = B.bug "gBool"
143    isBool  (VBool _)        = True
144    isBool  _                = False
145
146instance D.CDec BaalaC where
147    pDec                     = VDec
148    gDec (VDec x)            = x
149    gDec _                   = B.bug "gDec"
150    isDec  (VDec _)          = True
151    isDec  _                 = False
152
153instance D.CClock BaalaC where
154    pClock                   = VClock
155    gClock  (VClock x)       = x
156    gClock  _                = B.bug "gClock"
157    isClock (VClock _)       = True
158    isClock _                = False
159
160instance D.CTime BaalaC where
161    pTime                    = VTime
162    gTime  (VTime x)         = x
163    gTime  _                 = B.bug "gTime"
164    isTime (VTime _)         = True
165    isTime _                 = False
166
167instance D.CCode BaalaC where
168    pCode                    = VCode
169    gCode (VCode s)          = s
170    gCode _                  = B.bug "gCode"
171    isCode  (VCode _)        = True
172    isCode  _                = False
173
174instance D.CText BaalaC where
175    pText                    = VText
176    gText (VText s)          = s
177    gText _                  = B.bug "gText"
178    isText  (VText _)        = True
179    isText  _                = False
180
181instance D.CList BaalaC where
182    pList                    = VList
183    gList (VList xs)         = xs
184    gList _                  = []
185    isList (VList _)         = True
186    isList _                 = False

189-- ----------------------  koshu data

191instance D.CEmpty BaalaC where
192    empty                    = VEmpty
193    isEmpty VEmpty           = True
194    isEmpty _                = False
195
196instance D.CEnd BaalaC where
197    end                      = VEnd
198    isEnd VEnd               = True
199    isEnd _                  = False
200
201instance D.CTerm BaalaC where
202    pTerm                    = VTerm
203    gTerm (VTerm s)          = s
204    gTerm _                  = B.bug "gTerm"
205    isTerm  (VTerm _)        = True
206    isTerm  _                = False
207
208instance D.CInterp BaalaC where
209    pInterp                  = VInterp
210    gInterp (VInterp r)      = r
211    gInterp _                = B.bug "gInterp"
212    isInterp  (VInterp _)    = True
213    isInterp  _              = False
214
215instance D.CType BaalaC where
216    pType                    = VType
217    gType (VType r)          = r
218    gType _                  = B.bug "gType"
219    isType  (VType _)        = True
220    isType  _                = False
221
222instance D.CSet BaalaC where

224    gSet (VSet x)            = x
225    gSet _                   = B.bug "gSet"
226    isSet  (VSet _)          = True
227    isSet  _                 = False
